  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Champagne Blend</p>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mt-3">The prestige pick for gifting, anniversaries, and buyers who want a clear step up in depth and reputation. It brings more layered brioche, stone fruit, and length than standard house Brut, and it still feels familiar to non-collectors.</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-4">
